OL,3,CDrink and drug driver didn't stop
OL,4,Cafter killing cyclist while overtaking
OL,6,FA drink and drug driver killed a
OL,7,Fcyclist by overtaking a peloton of
OL,8,Fnine riders on a rural road.
OL,10,FJack Bingley, 26, was driving a van
OL,11,Falong Cottam Lane in Treswell, in the
OL,12,Fmorning of Sunday 28 January 2024,
OL,13,Fafter a night out.
OL,15,FHe decided to overtake a group of
OL,16,Fcyclists who were riding two abreast,
OL,17,Fbefore stretching into single file, in
OL,18,Fpreparation to make a right turn.
