OL,3,CDrink and drug driver didn't stop
OL,4,Cafter killing cyclist while overtaking
OL,6,FRobert Noble, 57, the chairman of the
OL,7,FTrent Vikings Cycling Club, was in the
OL,8,Fmiddle of the road as he had signalled
OL,9,Fto turn right.
OL,11,FHe was hit at speed by the overtaking
OL,12,Fvan, thrown into the air and landed in
OL,13,Fa roadside ditch. He died of his
OL,14,Finjuries.
OL,16,FA second rider was also clipped by the
OL,17,Fvan - he fell and suffered soft tissue
OL,18,Finjuries.
OL,20,FBingley, of Devonshire Road, Retford,
OL,21,Fdrove off after the collision.
