OL,3,CDrink and drug driver didn't stop
OL,4,Cafter killing cyclist while overtaking
OL,6,FHis passengers, who had urged him not
OL,7,Fto overtake, begged him to go back but
OL,8,Fhe ignored them and continued to drive
OL,9,Faway.
OL,11,FThey demanded he let them out, which
OL,12,Fhe did, before inspecting the damage
OL,13,Fto his van and driving off.
OL,15,FThe women returned to the scene and
OL,16,Ftold the police what had happened.
OL,18,FBingley returned to the scene a couple
OL,19,Fof hours later and identified himself
OL,20,Fto police.
