OL,3,CDrink and drug driver didn't stop
OL,4,Cafter killing cyclist while overtaking
OL,6,FHe tested over the limit for alcohol
OL,7,Fand was positive for cocaine or its
OL,8,Fmetabolites. He was arrested and
OL,9,Fsubsequently charged.
OL,11,FIt was later shown he would have been
OL,12,Fover twice the drink drive limit at
OL,13,Fthe time of the collision.
OL,15,FBingley appeared at Nottingham Crown
OL,16,FCourt for sentencing on Friday (16
OL,17,FAugust) after pleading guilty to
OL,18,Fcausing death by dangerous driving.
