OL,6,FHe was given a nine-year prison
OL,7,Fsentence and was banned from driving
OL,8,Ffor five years, starting from his
OL,9,Frelease from prison.
OL,11,FIn a statement the family of Mr Noble,
OL,12,Fwho was from Gainsborough,
OL,13,FLincolnshire, and who is survived by
OL,14,Fhis wife and four children, said: "Rob
OL,15,Fwas a larger-than-life figure, well-
OL,16,Fknown in the local community for his
OL,17,Fthunderous laugh and outgoing nature.
