OL,6,F"He was known to many through his
OL,7,Fplumbing, heating, and electrical
OL,8,Fbusiness, which carries on in his
OL,9,Fabsence - but also through ventures
OL,10,Fsuch as cycling clubs."
OL,12,FDetective Constable Andrew Fawcett, of
OL,13,FNottinghamshire Police, said: "Our
OL,14,Fthoughts are with Mr Noble's family
OL,15,Fand friends and his fellow cycle club
OL,16,Fmembers who are understandably
OL,17,Fdevastated by this incident.
