OL,6,F"This was a wholly unnecessary death
OL,7,Fcaused by Bingley's foolish and
OL,8,Fsenseless decision to drive whilst
OL,9,Fstill highly intoxicated and under the
OL,10,Finfluence of drink and drugs.
OL,12,F"This resulted in the selfish decision
OL,13,Fto overtake a group of cyclists when
OL,14,Fit was clearly unsafe to do so.
